==Yin Earth Rabbit (己卯)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)}}), the month of {{ill|February|ja|2月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Awakening of Insects|ja|啓蟄}} until the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明}}) as applicable.

==Yin Earth Rabbit (己卯)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu}} for {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯}} is as follows.
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯}} is the 2nd day of {{ill|Small Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土}}.


