In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|February|ja|2月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|lt=Awakening of Insects|ja|啓蟄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.
==Yin Earth Rabbit (己卯)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} for {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is as follows.
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 2nd day of {{ill|Small Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.


