==Yin Earth Rabbit (己卯)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|February|ja|2月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|lt=Awakening of Insects|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) as applicable.
==Yin Earth Rabbit (己卯)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} for {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is as follows.
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Kibou|ja|己卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is the 2nd day of {{ill|Small Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

