ata|lt=2239 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 23世紀|1=23rd century|WD=Q49832}} * {{ill|2299 AD|ja|2299年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2299|comment=changed title based on wikidata|lt=2299 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 23世紀|1=23rd century|WD=Q49832}} * {{ill|2359 AD|ja|2359年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2359|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2359 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2419 AD|ja|2419年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2419|comment=changed title based on wikidata|lt=2419 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 25世紀|1=25th century|WD=Q49839}} * {{ill|2479 AD|ja|2479年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2479|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2479 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2539 AD|ja|2539年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2539|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2539 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2599 AD|ja|2599年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2599|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2599 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2659 AD|ja|2659年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2659|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2659 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2719 AD|ja|2719年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2719|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2719 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2779 AD|ja|2779年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2779|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2779 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2839 AD|ja|2839年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2839|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2839 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2899 AD|ja|2899年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2899|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2899 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2959 AD|ja|2959年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2959|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2959 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |} ==Months of Yin Earth Rabbit== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|lt=Kanoe (庚)|2=ja|3=庚|4=zh|5=庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|lt=Kinoto (乙)|2=ja|3=乙|4=zh|5=乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (乙)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:February|February]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|month (calendar)]] of {{ill|Kibou|ja|1=Yin Earth Rabbit|2=ja|己卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Rabbit|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Jingzhe|Awakening of Insects]] until the day before [[:en:Qingming (solar term)|Qingming]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yin Earth Rabbit== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for {{ill|Kibou|ja|1=Yin Earth Rabbit|2=ja|己卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Rabbit|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} is as follows. === Selected Day (選日) === The day of {{ill|Kibou|ja|1=Yin Earth Rabbit|2=ja|己卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kibou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Rabbit|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} is the 2nd day of {{ill|Small Earth|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Small Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Small Earth|qq=|1=Tsuchi (Japanese term)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11571306}}.
